OL,3,CTeenage pedestrian in critical
OL,4,Ccondition after collision
OL,6,FA teenage pedestrian is in a critical
OL,7,Fcondition following a collision with a
OL,8,Fcar near Penrith on Friday night (1st
OL,9,FMay).
OL,11,FEmergency services were called to the
OL,12,Fscene on the A6 near Milestone House
OL,13,Faround 10pm and the pedestrian was
OL,14,Ftaken to hospital, where he remains.
OL,16,FThe incident involved a white Audi.
OL,18,FPolice say the driver stopped at the
OL,19,Fscene.
